    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it's basically brand new and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s in absolute pristine condition with zero scratches or dings. It drives like a total dream and is super clean inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
