    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a benchmark-standard BMW E46 M3 in museum-grade condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system. Mechanically impeccable, the vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement, a complete VANOS overhaul, and rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a 3.25:1 variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains rigid and the factory suspension geometry is laser-straight. This is a turn-key, investment-quality example for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
