    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is, without question, the finest example of this model currently available. From the moment you lay eyes on the deep, mirror-like finish of the original paint\u2014preserved since day one with a professional ceramic coating\u2014you will realize this car has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage its entire life. The interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma, with the premium leather upholstery showing absolutely no bolster wear, creasing, or fading. Every button, switch, and technological feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach; it comes with a documented, obsessive service history performed exclusively by master technicians using only genuine OEM parts. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage is remarkably spotless, free from any road debris or weathering. This is more than just a used car; it is a time capsule for the enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
